casebody.data:
Michael D. CREWS, Secretary, Florida Department of Corrections, petitioner,
v.
Anthony Joseph FARINA. No. 13-1227. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 10, 2014.

Opinion

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied.
